    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "怜、お疲れ様。渚は戻ってる？　今日誕生日だから\nプレゼントにダンスを練習して来たんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "怜、お疲れ様。渚は戻ってる？　今日誕生日だから\nプレゼントにダンスを練習して来たんだよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.6666665713,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9299.999999999998,
          "startTime": 16.9666665713
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12963.333333300001,
          "startTime": 20.6299999046
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "クイズ番組の収録を終えてもうすぐ戻るみたいだけど\n……『一ノ瀬怜　むっつり』っと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "クイズ番組の収録を終えてもうすぐ戻るみたいだけど\n……『一ノ瀬怜　むっつり』っと……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.5828432489,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "なんだかさっきからずっとスマホを触ってるね\n買い物？　欲しい物でもあるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "なんだかさっきからずっとスマホを触ってるね\n買い物？　欲しい物でもあるの？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0333332379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、SNSのチェックをしてるの\nちょっと気が気じゃないのよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ううん、SNSのチェックをしてるの\nちょっと気が気じゃないのよね……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5333332379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、仕事が終わったばかりなのに真面目だね、怜は\nじゃあ邪魔しないで、もう少し渚を待つことにするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そっか、仕事が終わったばかりなのに真面目だね、怜は\nじゃあ邪魔しないで、もう少し渚を待つことにするよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.466666317,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5066.666668400004,
          "startTime": 44.5333329854
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5033.3333333,
          "startTime": 44.4999996503
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7583.333682999999,
          "startTime": 47.05
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "今日のクイズ番組の収録楽しかったな～琴乃ちゃん\n千紗ちゃんも一緒のアイドル軍が大勝利したし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "今日のクイズ番組の収録楽しかったな～琴乃ちゃん\n千紗ちゃんも一緒のアイドル軍が大勝利したし",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "次の『アイドル vs 文化人』も楽しみだな～\nあれ……？　まだ誰かいる……もしかして葵ちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "次の『アイドル vs 文化人』も楽しみだな～\nあれ……？　まだ誰かいる……もしかして葵ちゃん？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11283.904314099991,
          "startTime": 65.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　なんで事務所で踊ってるの！？\nしかも一人で！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "えっ！？　なんで事務所で踊ってるの！？\nしかも一人で！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "渚を待ってたんだ。誕生日プレゼントにダンスを\n贈ろうと思ってね。この踊りを見て何か感じないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "渚を待ってたんだ。誕生日プレゼントにダンスを\n贈ろうと思ってね。この踊りを見て何か感じないかな？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7690361628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "はっ！　その妙な小股に不自然な腕の振りは――\nミュージカル映画『恋に焦ってみたり』のダンス！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "はっ！　その妙な小股に不自然な腕の振りは――\nミュージカル映画『恋に焦ってみたり』のダンス！？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ！　さぁ、もう止まらないよ！　渚も一緒に\n踊ろう！　映画の世界へhere we go！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そうだよ！　さぁ、もう止まらないよ！　渚も一緒に\n踊ろう！　映画の世界へhere we go！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.4106296063
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.4106296063
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.6606296063
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "嘘……初めて踊るはずなのに、自然と体が動くよ！\nあぁ！　なんて気持ちがいいんだろう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "嘘……初めて踊るはずなのに、自然と体が動くよ！\nあぁ！　なんて気持ちがいいんだろう！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.3999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.3999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "恋に恋焦がれる主人公ジェニファーの気持ちが流れ\n込んでくる！　私は渚？　それともジェニファー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "恋に恋焦がれる主人公ジェニファーの気持ちが流れ\n込んでくる！　私は渚？　それともジェニファー！？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.8333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.0939629396
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.666666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "その調子！　どんどん行くよ！　そーら\n次はこのステップだ！　let's dance！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "その調子！　どんどん行くよ！　そーら\n次はこのステップだ！　let's dance！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.0999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 128.433337911
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "これは！　ジェニファーが夏の海岸でいじめっ子達に\n見せつけた、エレガント・ステップだよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "これは！　ジェニファーが夏の海岸でいじめっ子達に\n見せつけた、エレガント・ステップだよね！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.7333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 134.7333358765
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 137.0143077375
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "それそれ！　さぁ、僕らも見せつけてやろうよ！\nあのいじめっ子達にさ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "それそれ！　さぁ、僕らも見せつけてやろうよ！\nあのいじめっ子達にさ！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.1000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 141.1000025432
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 144.166229741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁはぁ、もう最高！　It's the best！\nやっとジェニファーの本当の気持ちを理解出来たよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "はぁはぁ、もう最高！　It's the best！\nやっとジェニファーの本当の気持ちを理解出来たよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.9333307903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "僕もだよ。渚、ありがとう。遅くまで付き合ってくれて\nそして、ジェニファーにも感謝を述べるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "僕もだよ。渚、ありがとう。遅くまで付き合ってくれて\nそして、ジェニファーにも感謝を述べるよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.9333307903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "でも……そういえば、なんで踊り始めたんだっけ……？\n私、なんだか途中から陶酔しちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "でも……そういえば、なんで踊り始めたんだっけ……？\n私、なんだか途中から陶酔しちゃって……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.2666559856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "なんでだっけ？　確かに二人ともゾーンに入ってたから\n何はともあれ誕生日おめでと、渚",
      "translations": {
